=== HTTP REQUEST PARSING AND HANDLING ===
    Read and analyze incoming requests:
        ‚òê Extract HTTP method (`GET`, `POST`, `DELETE`)
        ‚òê Extract requested URL
        ‚òê Extract and store headers
        ‚òê Manage chunked and non-chunked requests
        ‚òê Extract request body (if present)
    Check validity of request:
        ‚òê Correct request (`200 OK`)
        ‚òê Invalid URL (`404 Not Found`)
        ‚òê Method not supported (`405 Method Not Allowed`)
