        ‚òê `Set-Cookie` (if needed)
    Manage common HTTP statuses:
        ‚òê `200 OK`
        ‚òê `400 Bad Request`
        ‚òê `403 Forbidden`
        ‚òê `404 Not Found`
        ‚òê `405 Method Not Allowed`
